# Pectin-Based Jellies Business Plan
**Launch Date:** June 6, 2025  
**Prepared for:** Brainwave Matrix Solutions  

---

## 1. Executive Summary  
Healthy, vegan jellies made from pectin (fruit-based) targeting:  
✔ Health-conscious consumers  
✔ Parents seeking clean-label snacks  
✔ Diabetics needing sugar-free options  

**Key Differentiators:**  
- 100% natural ingredients (no gelatin, artificial sweeteners)  
- Low-calorie, gluten-free, diabetic-friendly  
- Premium positioning at $3.99-$5.99 per pack  

